        "evidence": "<p>The Glasgow Alcoholic Hepatitis Score is calculated by the addition of the selected points:</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 454.648px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 66.6667%; height: 22.3984px;\"><strong>Variable</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\"><strong>Points</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 34.3906px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 64.789px;\">Age</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 34.3906px;\">&lt;50</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 34.3906px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 30.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 30.3984px;\">&ge;50</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 30.3984px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40.2266px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 85.4532px;\">White blood cell count</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 40.2266px;\">&lt;15 x10<sup>9</sup>/L</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 40.2266px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 45.2266px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 45.2266px;\">&ge;15 x10<sup>9</sup>/L</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 45.2266px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.375px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 65.75px; width: 33.3333%;\" rowspan=\"2\">BUN</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 33.375px;\">&lt;5 mmol/L</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 33.375px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32.375px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 32.375px;\">&ge;5 mmol/L</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 32.375px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 38.375px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 108.125px; width: 33.3333%;\" rowspan=\"3\">Bilirubin</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 38.375px;\">&lt;125 &mu;mol/L</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 38.375px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.375px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 